OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779966178
OL,3,C'Wild west for tech firms': Ex-Ofcom
OL,4,Cboss backs under-16s social media ban
OL,6,FGrade compares social media companies
OL,7,Fto tobacco firms: hugely profitable
OL,8,Fbusinesses built on products that can
OL,9,Fcause harm.
OL,11,F"Self-regulation has failed because
OL,12,Fthey don't know the meaning of the
OL,13,Fword," he told ITV News.
OL,15,FThe major tech companies, he argues,
OL,16,Fhave enjoyed a "wild west" for too
OL,17,Flong, pursuing "clicks and advertising
OL,18,Frevenue" while allowing a "toxic
OL,19,Fcorner" of the internet to flourish.
OL,26,@sD@AOUuD@FO]xD@POUxD@ZO]yD@POUzD@HO]zD@
OL,26,A[OU{D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779966178
OL,3,C'Wild west for tech firms': Ex-Ofcom
OL,4,Cboss backs under-16s social media ban
OL,6,FThe central problem, Grade says, is
OL,7,Fthat children are no longer in control
OL,8,Fof what they see online.
OL,10,FAlgorithms decide what is pushed at
OL,11,Fthem. The Molly Russell case, he said,
OL,12,Fexposed the "unscrupulous" and
OL,13,F"addictive" nature of parts of social
OL,14,Fmedia.
OL,16,FGrade is not a natural
OL,17,Finterventionist. He served as chair of
OL,18,FOfcom from 2022 to 2026, but is a
OL,19,Flifelong free-marketeer and advocate
OL,20,Fof light-touch regulation.
OL,26,@tD@MOUtD@ZO]uD@AOUuD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/20
