OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779966178
OL,3,C'Wild west for tech firms': Ex-Ofcom
OL,4,Cboss backs under-16s social media ban
OL,6,FMichael Grade says under-16s should be
OL,7,Fbanned from accessing social media
OL,9,FHe said he came to support a ban only
OL,10,Fafter concluding that the major tech
OL,11,Fcompanies - like Meta (which owns
OL,12,FInstagram and Facebook), Google (which
OL,13,Fowns YouTube), TikTok, Snap and X -
OL,14,Fwere resistant to change.
OL,16,F"I think it will call the tech
OL,17,Fcompanies to account," he said. "It'll
OL,18,Faffect their revenues - and there's
OL,19,Fnothing worse for these companies than
OL,20,Fhurting their revenue."
OL,26,@xD@AOUyD@VO]yD@aOU|D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/20
