OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779966178
OL,3,C'Wild west for tech firms': Ex-Ofcom
OL,4,Cboss backs under-16s social media ban
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"It's a matter for Parliament," Grade
OL,12,Finsists. "If they don't like it,
OL,13,Finstead of complaining about it,
OL,14,Feither take action or keep quiet."
OL,16,FOfcom is currently investigating
OL,17,Fwhether GB News breached broadcasting
OL,18,Frules in an interview last year with
OL,19,FPresident Trump.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@_O]tD@JOUvD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/20
