OL,3,C'Wild west for tech firms': Ex-Ofcom
OL,4,Cboss backs under-16s social media ban
OL,6,F"As far as I'm concerned, GB News
OL,7,Foperates under exactly the same rules
OL,8,Fas ITN, the BBC and Sky News. They
OL,9,Fhave to show due impartiality at all
OL,10,Ftimes, which they do, irrespective of
OL,11,Fwho the presenter is."
